name: Clean Seas #TeamSeas #SEAJAM
description:
A Game About Picking up trash from The Oceans! Drive your Trash Eating Robot around the sea collecting as much trash as possible.

Also Includes 2 Modes:

  • Clean Mode || Collect trash without any time limit!
  • Rush Mode || Collect as much trash in 60 Seconds as possible!
